   LIVE Webcasting of Committee Hearings and Markups

   The Committee on Education and the Workforce is now providing LIVE
   webcasting coverage of our hearings and markups.

   For the schedule of webcasting events please see our Committee Schedule

           Hand holding a video camera    View the current Webcast

   You will need Windows Media Player to view the event.  You can download
   Media Player (link opens a new browser window) for free by clicking on
                               the icon below:

   Go to Windows Media Player download web site - link opens a new browser
